<ol class="breadcrumb breadcrumb-arrow">
	<li><%= link_to 'Home', root_path %></li>
	<li class="active"><span>About</span></li>
</ol>
<div class="banner parbase section">
  <section class="banner-component has-responsive-height has-background has-content-width-background">
    <div class="banner-background gradient blue-base"></div>
    <div class="banner-content content-margin">
      <div class="banner-content-container banner-content-align-center manual-content-position from-2 to-23">
          <p class="banner-headline headline-66">About Us</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
<div class="content-margin">
  <div class="flexible-column-frame-columns">
    <section class="flexible-column-frame-column">
      <div class="full-rich-text parbase section">
        <section class="rich-text rich-text-mode-reader">
          <p>
            Purpose: To have a platform where college students, the next generation, can promote their own business at affordable prices.
          </p>

          <p><strong>Things to know:</strong></p>

          <p>
            TheFutureAreUS was founded in 2017 in order to help promote entrepreneurial college students.
          </p>

          <p>
            ONLY students can use this database with a school issued email, in support of local student owned businesses.
          </p>

          <p>
            TheFurtureAreUS makes money, by having student entrepreneurs pay a subscription to post ads, AND by selling ads to local businesses.
          </p>

          <p>
            In order to use the database, you must register with us first and it is free to register and find student owned businesses.
          </p>

          <p>
            You may post reviews on a business and refer a student owned business as well.
          </p>

          <p>
            All Student entrepreneurs who pay for a subscription must first be approved before we promote their business on the site.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
